What kind of monitor is it? Most 1360x768 pixel widescreens that I've seen are TVs, and TVs tend to be big. Or is your monitor a 1024x600 panel in a netbook?<br /><br />Does zooming in a web page also zoom in objects rendered by plug-ins (e.g. SWF, Java)?<br /><br />As for the fuzziness, try Display Properties &gt; Appearance &gt; Effects and see if playing with the ClearType setting does anything.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Thu Aug 27, 2009 6:12 am</p><hr />
